    "body": "The removed header includes have not been needed since https://github.com/bitcoin-core/secp256k1/pull/1231.\r\n\r\nTest suggestions:\r\n1. Using Autotools-based build system:\r\n```\r\n./autogen.sh\r\n./configure\r\nmake clean-precomp\r\nmake\r\n```\r\n2. Using CMake-based build system:\r\n```\r\ncmake -B build -DCMAKE_C_INCLUDE_WHAT_YOU_USE=\"include-what-you-use\"\r\ncmake --build build --target secp256k1_precomputed\r\n```",
